Summary: Minimising / restoring inactive windows loses (Inactive) in title
Class: bug
Difficulty: fun
Priority: low
Content-type: text/plain

If a PuTTY session ends and the window sticks around, the titlebar is
changed to PuTTY (Inactive).  When the window is minimised and
restored, the titlebar is changed back to the title the window had
before the session ended.
